🌤️ Weather App
A simple weather application that allows users to check real-time weather conditions for any city using the OpenWeatherMap API. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, the app is designed to be fully responsive on all devices.

🚀 Features
✅ Fetch real-time weather updates
✅ Displays temperature, humidity, and weather conditions
✅ User-friendly interface
✅ Fully responsive (mobile, tablet, and desktop)
✅ Lightweight and fast

🖥️ Responsive Design
The app is designed with mobile-first principles and works seamlessly on all devices.

Key Techniques Used:
✅ CSS Flexbox & Grid for layout
✅ Media Queries for responsiveness
✅ Viewport Meta Tag for mobile compatibility


